animeDescription: Assorted Mameshiba shorts that are not a part of the regular episodes nor new series or collaborations.Includes:Mamerry Christmas-hen (Christmas caroling, claymation)5-Shuunen Party-hen (5th Mameversary, claymation)Sakamichi Korokoro-hen (Mameshiba rolling down a hill)Kansatsu-hen (Mameshiba being looked at under a magnifying glass)Music Clip (a Mameshiba music video promoting the official YouTube channel launching)
